Package org.jfree.beans.events

Events and listeners.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CategoryItemClickListener A listener for item clicks on a AbstractCategoryChart.
LegendClickListener A listener for series clicks on a legend.
SectionClickListener A listener for section clicks on a JPieChart.
XYItemClickListener A listener for item clicks on a AbstractXYChart.
 

Class Summary
CategoryItemClickEvent An event object that carries information about a mouse click on an item in an AbstractCategoryChart.
LegendClickEvent An event object that carries information about a mouse click on a series in a legend.
SectionClickEvent An event object that carries information about a mouse click on a section in a JPieChart.
XYItemClickEvent An event object that carries information about a mouse click on an item in an AbstractXYChart.
